                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/2983: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Feely</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-03-30T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 30, 1933—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>7. Your 25, March 30, noon, last paragraph. There is no justification for Finot’s
                    statement. The Commission supported fully the suggestions of the neighboring
                    countries for an armistice and would be very glad to see the efforts of the
                    neighboring countries succeed in reestablishing peace and bringing about a
                    settlement of the Chaco matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
